title._content: Stewart's plan for improving the plaza.

description._content: Repository: California Historical Society Digital object ID: Kemble Spec Col 09_B263 Call Number: Kemble Spec Col 09 Collection: California Lettersheet Collection Date: Undated Physical Description: Wood engraving; 13 x 20 cm. General Note: Engraved for F.C.M. Fenn & Co., 203 Clay Street, by A.V.S. Anthony. Scope and Contents: Illustrates Stewart's Baroque-Classical plan for improving the San Francisco Plaza, which was never executed. Preferred citation: Stewart's plan for improving the plaza, California Lettersheet Collection, Kemble Spec Col 09, courtesy, California Historical Society, Kemble Spec Col 09_B263.
